<h2>Vendor account update</h2>

<p>Hello {{name}},</p>
<p>We've reviewed your vendor registration request.</p>
<p>Unfortunately, we're unable to approve your vendor account at this time.</p>

{{#if reason}}
<div class="danger-box">
  <p><strong>Reason:</strong> {{reason}}</p>
</div>
{{/if}}

<p style="color: #71717a; font-size: 14px;">
  Questions? <a href="{{frontendUrl}}/support" style="color: #ea580c; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none;">Contact our support team</a>.
</p>
